  <p>
    All v0.9.x features are <strong>opt-in</strong> and fully backward-compatible. Your existing <code>AraxysConfig</code> continues to work unchanged. New modules (MFA, RBAC, OAuth2, Admin API, PostgreSQL pool) only activate when their config sections are populated.
